.PP
The
.B ipopt
flags control the delivery and transmission of IP options.
When
.B NWUO_EN_IPOPT
is set IP, options will be delivered and sent.
When
.B NWUO_DI_IPOPT
is set IP option will be stripped from received packets and no IP options will
be sent.
